Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Infiltration is a success.\NThat was quite easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone is disturbing my rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This chakra... He is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.17,0:01:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right, where do I search first?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.90,0:01:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have one of these, Granny...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.46,0:01:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen your face before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.99,0:01:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... I'm a writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.71,0:01:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I travel around and write about \Nregional cuisine and products for a magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I see.\NAnd how do you like my pork buns?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.07,0:01:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, they're delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.93,0:01:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about them,\Nand they're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to introduce them\Nin our magazine. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.48,0:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In a magazine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:02:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Although, once I write about them,\N you'll have such a big crowd you won't be able to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I see. That would be a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is peaceful around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.02,0:02:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This village is no longer plagued by war\Nthanks to Lord Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're so grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.17,0:02:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Lord Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.11,0:02:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to\NHanzo of the Salamander?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.54,0:02:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanzo of the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your time, Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.84,0:02:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.68,0:02:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that is Lady Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,They say it's good fortune to put up origami\N shaped after the Lady Angel at the shop entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,An Angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is going on?\N{\i1}This land isn't divided into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.69,0:03:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Instead it's already united.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Hidden Rain Village {\i1}used to have\N a leader {\i1}named Hanzo of the Salamander...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.24,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems I need to check\N{\i1}this place out very thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's going to be\Nan intense battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.24,0:03:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely, you jest...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't tell lies. All of it is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.32,0:03:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.46,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what an intense battle this is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You have good taste for\Nchoosing me, Mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well Tezuna, you look just\Nlike someone I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your names are similar too,\Nso I couldn't help but request for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.70,0:04:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was well worth the long journey here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're not from around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, well I heard there might be work\Nfor a mercenary like me, so I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If I recall,\Nit was Hanzo of the Salamander who...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shh! Don't talk about such things here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If they think you're one of\NHanzo's associates, you'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.10,0:04:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... That's disturbing news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The new leader, Lord Pain, is very strict...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll show no mercy to anyone he suspects.\N That is what my hubby says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you married, Tezuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... My hubby is just a village genin\Nand doesn't earn much. I have to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's harsh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,According to my hubby,\N Lord Pain makes it rain in this village with his jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.22,0:05:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain can tell him\Nwhat everybody is doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.43,0:05:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... That's a scary jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's better to watch\Nwhat we talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tezuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.84,0:05:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.81,0:05:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm already under his watch...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm coming home now with\Na present"? Yeah right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably buying something\Nat the gift shop by Shibuki Bridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! What a sad piece of writing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Konan... When I stop the rain,\Nseek out the intruder with your jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.47,0:06:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.07,0:06:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.17,0:06:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What a downpour.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.21,0:06:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna get a drink while\Nwe wait for the rain to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.79,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no bars at\Na low ground level like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have to go up higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's head upwards\Nfor some cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.53,0:06:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.04,0:06:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you tell your wife\Nyou're heading straight home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.22,0:06:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! It's okay.\NIt's an emergency mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I never heard of drinking\Nbeing a mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,GRAND OPENING\NCLUB FROG
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh... We're in luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Just two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us sake and some chasers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's not Sunday, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.93,0:07:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must have come up\Nfor Lord Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's leaving for another nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it never rained on other days before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's something that\Nrequires that much power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But if it keeps on raining like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Careful with the words!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Pain works tirelessly\Nfor the people of this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Show some tolerance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you fellows waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.21,0:07:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.66,0:07:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no... You're in luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:08:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we have\Nour grand opening special.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.17,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of service?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The Club Frog Special Torture Service.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.91,0:08:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You...! Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.28,0:08:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one asking the questions.\NAnd I have a lot to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.98,0:08:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.06,0:10:21.40,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(737.813,586.25)}Infiltrate!\N{\i1}The Village Hidden in the Rain\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it, Konan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.89,0:11:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,From your use of kunai,\NI'm guessing you two are lowly ninjas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that rogue ninja mark signify\Nthat you're loyal to Pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the belly of a frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll never be found here...\NNo one will come to your aid!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I'll be the one\Nasking questions. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you gonna do\Nwith that feather?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickle you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to die laughing,\Nthen you'll answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.53,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding your leader...Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now talk! Tell me everything\Nyou know about Pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Bear with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't...rat...on my comrade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty stubborn, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have another trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If you refuse to talk, then I'll use my jutsu\Nand {\i1}flog{\i0} you to frogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Flog...you...to frogs...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.67,0:12:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want from us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be lowly ninjas,\Nbut we'll never betray our comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.25,0:12:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do to us!\NSo don't take us lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:13:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Then I have no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ninja Art! Toad Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.55,0:13:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, you're next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.36,0:13:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The highest tower in the west...\NLord Pain is there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what people say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What?! You sure turned\Non him easily...didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.21,0:13:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, no matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you mean by,\N"that's what people say"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually... No one really knows\Nthat much about Lord Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.58,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They say he is from Fuma Clan lineage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one really knows\Nwhat he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.14,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And some claim that\Nhe doesn't even exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.02,0:14:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked through the town a bit...\Nand everyone seems to worship him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.15,0:14:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.41,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In this town, Lord Pain is a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a question of whether\Nhe exists or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.70,0:14:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He always watches over us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a representative do all the ceremonial\N rites, the speeches and the issuing of orders...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the Lady Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.11,0:14:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Angel...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.48,0:14:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's your leader, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Why must he hide his appearances\Nfrom you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.87,0:14:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,For times like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a remnant of\Nthe old Hidden Rain, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about\Nthe old Hidden Rain remnants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... You really don't know\Na thing, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.98,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're an outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Until recently,\Nthose remnants would infiltrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not a worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only lucky fellows like you ever\Nmanage to slip in from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.28,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a worry? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that this land was\Ngoing through a civil war...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not surprising that you haven't heard.\N This nation is closed to the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The civil war ended long ago.\NAnd we won!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why Lord Pain is legendary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He destroyed the Hidden Rain...\Nby himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how powerful this Pain might be,\N the leader of the Hidden Rain was Hanzo of the Salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's not a soul in\Nthe ninja world that doesn't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But not only was Hanzo powerful,\Nhe was extremely cautious
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.87,0:16:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and made it very difficult for anyone\Nto approach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He had bodyguards on 24-hour duty,\Nand everyone, including children,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who went near him were strip searched.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.91,0:16:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So how did he defeat Hanzo?\NWhat ability does Pain possess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you. We don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think you would drive me\N{\i1}into a corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are young, but capable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I predict the Hidden Leaf shall\N{\i1}emerge victorious from this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Therefore, I shall let you three live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We don't want your sympathy!\N{\i1}We can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiraiya, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.88,0:16:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You three are strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.20,0:16:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And you managed to survive\N{\i1}and give me a tough time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.41,0:16:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will give you time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:17:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Become stronger and\N{\i1}come fight me again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In exchange for your lives,\N{\i1}tell me your names.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiraiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tsunade!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Orochimaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your names have been carved\N{\i1}into my memory...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Jiraiya! Tsunade! Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.68,0:17:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I, Hanzo, hereby name you\N{\i1}the "Hidden Leaf's Sannin."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it...\NHe defeated Hanzo by himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.48,0:17:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a god. He wields formidable jutsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But that is not why Lord Pain\Nis to be feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.35,0:17:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What is truly frightening is\Nhis merciless heart of steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone who threatened his ideals\Nwas ruthlessly extinguished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't stop with just Hanzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanzo's parents, his wife and child...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,His relatives and friends,\Nand even their infants, were killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he burned down their homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And he killed the emissaries of villages\Nallied with Hanzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He erased them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It was retribution...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.98,0:18:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a god, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.21,0:18:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A god...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.18,0:18:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, just what is your god\Ntrying to accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.77,0:18:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even underlings like you must know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the work of a god.\NWe wouldn't know what he plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Then if not god...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:19:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,you must at least know\Nsomething about the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Never heard of such a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Your arms and legs are bound,\Nso that you cannot move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pulse is being measured.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you lie, I'll know instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.25,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, you will end up surviving off\N dragonflies and flies for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.81,0:20:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now then...\N{\i1}Time to hunt the infiltrator.
